_sText:
This is my first map. I hope you enjoy! :)

I just wanted to create a special small map for trainings like famous map "$2000". But, while I was creating it, I understood, that it would better to make the structure of my map more difficult. So, here is a result.

You can find a scheme of this map in screenshots. It will show you the detailed map structure.

### **It is better to play in small teams (2-6 players in one team).** 

### **Average round duration: 30~5 seconds.**



_ **If you like it - rate this submission!** _

_ **Comments and wishes (and even critic:) are welcome!** _
 
P.S Sorry for my letterless english. I am from Russia).
